            "id": "4bda2a46fe0f4ca09062e",
            "questionText": "A rower applies a forward force of $!$180\\ N$!$ to propel a boat. Opposing forces include a drag force of $!$60\\ N$!$ and an air resistance of $!$20\\ N$!$. Given that the total mass of the boat and the rower is $!$100\\ kg$!$, calculate the acceleration of the boat.",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "3e5936b3f86c4c4492ba7",
                    "stepText": "Let's start by calculating the net force acting on the boat. Begin by combining the opposing forces and then subtracting from the forward force applied by the rower. What is the net force?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        "100"
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "N",
                    "stepConcepts": [
